<p class="casamiento">&hellip; and it doesn't stop at just names! Take the pain out of preparing your invitations by letting me individually address each envelope and invitation with the name and address of each of your guests. Not only will it look <span style="letter-spacing:0.2em; font-size:1em;font-family:'Gara';font-variant:small-caps">PROFESSIONAL</span>, but it'll save you a lot of hassle&mdash;you'd be surprised how time-consuming and frustrating it is addressing just 25 invitations without making a mistake or missing a guest. All you have to do is a send a list of names and addresses&hellip;
